             sworn.</p>
               <p>(The note shewn him.)</p>
               <p>This is not my hand writing. (The note shewn to the court.) I never sent any such note: I am servant to Mr. 
               <persName id="t17900915-115-person1137">
                  Josiah
                   Spode
