            : the prisoner was a servant of Mr. Spode's about five months ago.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17900915-115-person1138">
                  JOSIAH
                   SPODE
               <interp inst="t17900915-115-person1138" type="surname" value="SPODE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900915-115-person1138" type="given" value="JOSIAH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900915-115-person1138" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I never gave any orders for any wine glasses: I was on a journey at that time.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I have never been in the prosecutor's shop these eight months, since I left Mr. Spode's service.</p>
               <p>Mrs. Goodwin. I am sure he is the man; the first time I saw him I said, he was not the man; but on seeing him again, I said, he was the man; I had seen him twice or three times, when he was in Mr. Spode's service.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17900915-115-verdict602" type="verdictDescription">
